trans-unit.source: Defines the HTTP version numbers that are supported by the <see cref="T:System.Net.HttpWebRequest" /> and <see cref="T:System.Net.HttpWebResponse" /> classes.
trans-unit.target: 定義 <see cref="T:System.Net.HttpWebRequest" /> 和 <see cref="T:System.Net.HttpWebResponse" /> 類別 (Class) 支援的 HTTP 版本號碼。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Net.HttpVersion> class defines the HTTP versions that are supported by the <xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest> and <xref:System.Net.HttpWebResponse> classes.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Net.HttpVersion>類別定義所支援的 HTTP 版本<xref:System.Net.HttpWebRequest>和<xref:System.Net.HttpWebResponse>類別。

trans-unit.source: The HTTP version number is used to control version-specific features of HTTP, such as pipelining and chunking.
trans-unit.target: HTTP 版本號碼用來控制的 HTTP，例如管線和區塊處理的特定版本的功能。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the use of <xref:System.Net.HttpVersion>.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例示範 <xref:System.Net.HttpVersion> 的用法。
